pesticide.PPE: Long-sleeved shirt and long pants; Shoes plus socks; Protective eyewear including tight fitting goggles or face shield; Chemical-resistant gloves made of barrier laminate or butyl rubber ≥14 mils
pesticide.company_name: PRIME SOURCE, A DIVISION OF ALBAUGH LLC

Safety_Information.general_Info: WARNING. Causes substantial but temporary eye injury. Harmful if swallowed. Do not get in eyes or on clothing. Harmful if absorbed through skin. Wear protective eyewear including goggles, face shield, or safety glasses. Wash thoroughly with soap and water after handling and before eating, drinking, chewing gum, using tobacco, or using the toilet. Remove and wash contaminated clothing before reuse.
Safety_Information.if_In_Eyes: Hold eye open and rinse slowly and gently with water for 15-20 minutes. Remove contact lenses, if present, after the first 5 minutes, then continue rinsing eye. Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.if_Swallowed: Call a poison control center or doctor immediately for treatment advice. Have person sip a glass of water if able to swallow. Do not induce vomiting unless told to do so by a poison control center or doctor. Do not give anything by mouth to an unconscious person.
Safety_Information.if_On_Skin: Take off contaminated clothing. Rinse skin immediately with plenty of water for 15-20 minutes. Call a poison control center or doctor for treatment advice.
Safety_Information.physician_Note: Probably mucosal damage may contraindicate the use of gastric lavage.
